name: Antec AR-352 350W Power Supply for NSK 1380 microATX Case

reviews.name: Antec AR-352 350W Power Supply for NSK 1380 microATX Case
reviews.reviewText: Needed to replace my aging Antec Aria power supply and wanted to keep same case. The AR-352 fit perfectly and provided an upgrade, has more wattage, is quieter and has addtional SATA connector in harness compared to older AR-350
reviews.title: Perfect replacement for Antec Aria power supply

reviews.name: Antec AR-352 350W Power Supply for NSK 1380 microATX Case
reviews.reviewText: AR-300 power supply died in my Antec Aria case that I use for my HTPC. Wasn't sure if the AR-352 would fit, but it was a perfect fit and it is rated at 350 watts instead of 300 for the dead power supply.
reviews.title: Perfect replacement

reviews.name: Antec AR-352 350W Power Supply for NSK 1380 microATX Case
reviews.reviewText: Only fits in my Antec case. So not applicable to generic power supply. Instructions would have helped but I figured it out.
reviews.title: Perfect to replace my previous one

reviews.name: Antec AR-352 350W Power Supply for NSK 1380 microATX Case
reviews.reviewText: Just installed 10 days ago so can't say how long it will hold up. But its a PERFECT fit for a defunct antec AR-350 and the size was top priority. And it has 50 more watts. Price was excellent and I had it shipped to store so no cost. If it holds up for 6 more months, it will have been worth it for me. Anything more is just icing.
reviews.title: Good value for the money if it lasts
